		<h2 class='diff-currentversion-title'>Revision as of 16:38, 8 October 2014</h2>
<p>The <b>Receiver of Wreck</b> is an official who administers law dealing with wreck and salvage in some countries having a British administrative heritage.</p>
<p></p>
